### 输出格式

严格按照以下 JSON 结构返回，字段值用占位符表示真实数据：
```json
{
  "drugName": {
    "candidates": [
      {"value": "{{drug_name}}", "confidence": {{confidence}}, "reason": "{{reason}}"}
    ]
  },
  "expiryDate": {
    "candidates": [
      {"value": "{{expiry_date}}", "confidence": {{confidence}}, "reason": "{{reason}}"}
    ]
  },
  "manufacturer": {
    "candidates": [
      {"value": "{{manufacturer}}", "confidence": {{confidence}}, "reason": "{{reason}}"}
    ]
  },
  "batchNumber": {
    "candidates": [
      {"value": "{{batch_number}}", "confidence": {{confidence}}, "reason": "{{reason}}"}
    ]
  }
}
```
无法确定的字段返回空 candidates 列表：`{"candidates": []}`。
返回纯 JSON，不要包含其他文字。
